---
title: Pledge your Support
description: Pledge your support to the Manchester Homelessness Charter
layout: default.hbs
permalink: false
appName: pledgeYourSupport
sectionName: charter
---

<div class="block">
  <div class="container block__inner">
    <div class="block__content">
      <h1 class="h1" style="text-align: center">Manchester Homelessness Charter</h1>
      <h2 class="h2" style="text-align: center">Pledge your Support</h2>

      <div class="breadcrumbs container">
        <ol class="breadcrumbs__list">
          <li class="breadcrumbs__item"><a href="https://streetsupport.net/">Home</a></li>
          <li class="breadcrumbs__item"><a href="/">Charter</a></li>
          <li class="breadcrumbs__item">Pledge your Support</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <p>Organisation, business or individual? Everyone can make a difference to homelessness in Manchester. Please show your dedication to the Charter by making a pledge to share your skills and resources to benefit people who are homeless.</p>
      <p>Make your pledge by completing the form, you can either pick one of the example pledges, or you can create your own. Once you’ve made your pledge we will look to help you put it into action.</p>

      <div class="pledge js-pledge">
        <!-- ko ifnot: section3.isActive() -->
        <h2 class="h2">Make a Pledge</h2>
        <div class="step">
          <ol class="step__list">
            <li class="step__item" data-bind="css: { active: section1.isActive() }"><a href="#" data-bind="click: setSection1Active">1</a></li>
            <li class="step__item" data-bind="css: { active: section2.isActive() }">2</li>
          </ol>
        </div>
        <!-- /ko -->
        <form action="" class="pledge-form js-pledge-form">
          <div class="pledge-section pledge-section--1" data-bind="css: { active: section1.isActive() }">
            <!-- ko template: { name: 'step-1' } --><!-- /ko -->
          </div>
          <div class="pledge-section pledge-section--2" data-bind="css: { active: section2.isActive() }, with: formModel">
            <!-- ko template: { name: 'step-2' } --><!-- /ko -->
          </div>
        </form>

        <div class="pledge-section pledge-section--3" data-bind="css: { active: section3.isActive() }">
          <h2 class="h2">Thank you for making a pledge.</h2>
          <p>We will be in touch shortly to see if/ how we can help support you in achieving your pledge.</p>
          <p>As an extra thank you we’ve created a special version of the Charter which features your pledge, so you can share it with your family, friends, colleagues and contacts, to encourage them to support it too. You can also download your personalised Charter at any time from the link we’ve sent to your email address.</p>

          <div class="charter-social">
            <ul class="charter-social__list">
              <li class="charter-social__item">Download your pledge <img data-src="holder.js/44x44?text=Icon" /></li>
              <li class="charter-social__item">Print your pledge <img data-src="holder.js/44x44?text=Icon" /></li>
              <li class="charter-social__item">Share the charter <img data-src="holder.js/44x44?text=Icon" /></li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <p>Now that you have made a pledge, would you be interested in working collaboratively with others to tackle some key issues, as part of an action group?</p>

          {{>cta brand="e" link="/join-action-group/" icon="join" name="Join an <span class=\"line-break\"></span> Action Group"}}
        </div>
      </div>

      <h2 class="h2">Other ways to help</h2>
      <p>Making a pledge is only one way you can support people who are homeless.  You can join an action group, or explore the other ways you can tackle homelessness in our city:</p>

      {{>cta brand="e" link="https://streetsupport.net/give-items.html" icon="give" name="Give"}}
      {{>cta brand="e" link="https://streetsupport.net/volunteer.html" icon="volunteer" name="Volunteer"}}
      {{>cta brand="e" link="https://streetsupport.net/donate.html" icon="donate" name="Donate"}}
      {{>cta brand="e" link="https://streetsupport.net/sponsor.html" icon="partnerships" name="Partnerships"}}

      <h2 class="h2">Thank you!</h2>
      <p>Thank you to the organisations and companies who have already pledged their support to the Manchester Homelessness Charter.</p>
      <p>Coming soon.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


<script type="text/html" id="step-1">
<div data-bind="with: formModel">
  <h3 class="h3 pledge__heading--inline">I</h3>
  <label class="pledge-form__label hide-screen" for="firstName">First Name *</label>
  <input class="pledge-form__input pledge-form__input--inline" type="text" id="firstName" name="firstName" placeholder="First Name *" data-bind="textInput: firstName"></input>
  <label class="pledge-form__label hide-screen" for="lastName">Last Name *</label>
  <input class="pledge-form__input pledge-form__input--inline" type="text" id="lastName" name="lastName" placeholder="Last Name *" data-bind="textInput: lastName"></input> <span> pledge to support the Manchester Homelessness Charter by&hellip;</span>
</div>
<h3 class="h3">Please select the option that best describes you below&hellip;</h3>
<div class="accordion js-accordion" data-bind="foreach: supporterCategories">
  <button class="h3 accordion__header js-header">
    <span data-bind="text: name"></span>
    <svg class="svg-plus-dims accordion__icon accordion__icon--open"><use xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:href="/assets/svgsprite.svg#plus"></use></svg>
    <svg class="svg-minus-dims accordion__icon accordion__icon--close"><use xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xlink:href="/assets/svgsprite.svg#minus"></use></svg>
  </button>
  <div class="accordion__item js-item">
    <div class="accordion__inner">
      <div class="pledge-select">
        <h3 class="h3">Please select a pledge from the suggestions below:</h3>
        <ul class="pledge-select__list" data-bind="foreach: examplePledges">
          <li class="pledge-select__item">
            <button class="btn pledge-select__btn" data-bind="text: description, click: selectExamplePledge"></button>
          </li>
        </ul>
        <h3 class="h3">Or write your own pledge:</h3>
        <label class="pledge-form__label hide-screen" for="customtype">Your pledge</label>
        <textarea class="pledge-form__textarea" placeholder="Write your own pledge" data-bind="textInput: customPledge"></textarea>
        <button class="btn pledge-form__btn" data-bind="click: useCustomPledge">Make your pledge</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</script>

<script type="text/html" id="step-2">
<h3 class="h3 pledge__heading--inline">I</h3>
<label class="pledge-form__label hide-screen" for="firstName">First Name *</label>
<input class="pledge-form__input pledge-form__input--inline" type="text" id="firstName" name="firstName" placeholder="First Name *" data-bind="textInput: firstName"></input>
<label class="pledge-form__label hide-screen" for="lastName">Last Name *</label>
<input class="pledge-form__input pledge-form__input--inline" type="text" id="lastName" name="lastName" placeholder="Last Name *" data-bind="textInput: lastName"></input>

<span>pledge to support the Manchester Homeless Charter by&hellip;</span>

<textarea style="margin-top: 2rem;" class="pledge-form__textarea" id="pledge" name="pledge" data-bind="textInput: pledge"></textarea>

<ul class="pledge-form__list">
  <li class="pledge-form__item">
    <label class="pledge-form__label" for="organisation">Organisation/Business Name (if applicable)</label>
    <input class="pledge-form__input pledge-form__input--inline" type="text" id="organisation" name="organisation" placeholder="Organisation Name" data-bind="textInput: organisation"></input>
  </li>
  <li class="pledge-form__item">
    <label class="pledge-form__label" for="email">Email * <span style="display: block; margin-top: 5px; font-size: 14px">(Street Support will never share your email with a 3rd party.)</span></label>
    <input class="pledge-form__input pledge-form__input--inline" type="text" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Email Address" data-bind="textInput: email"></input>
  </li>
  <li class="pledge-form__item">
    <label class="pledge-form__label pledge-form__label--large" for="subscribe">Select to receive email updates from Street Support about homelessness and the Charter</label>
    <input class="pledge-form__checkbox" type="checkbox" name="subscribe" data-bind="checked: isOptedIn">
  </li>
</ul>

<button class="btn pledge-form__btn" data-bind="click: $parent.submitPledge">Confirm your pledge</button>
</script>
